2002-05-11 05:15  greg

	* Makefile, dip.c, dip.h, global.c, history.c, mail.c, mail.h,
	ml_set.c, phase.c, st_build.c, st_porder.c: Minor bug fixes - fixed
	subjectline for absence requests - fixed phase length, so it's no
	longer hard coded for responses - partial fix for unusable builds,
	players with only unusable builds    will no longer be flagged as
	having orders due, however players    with some usable builds will
	need to waive any unusable builds,    also, if one or more players
	have unusable builds, but no	player has usable builds, the build
	phase will process after    a short delay

