	* rdip.c: Passing of config_dir setting to dip, use of syslogging

2000-11-14 09:27  miller

	* conf.c: Added new dip.conf variables

2000-11-14 09:27  miller

	* mail.h: Added a few extra glags and a couple of defines to force
	password of resigned payers to a bad value

2000-11-14 09:27  miller

	* params.c: Display of all new additional parameters

2000-11-14 09:27  miller

	* ml_signon.c: Small changes for Blind/Wings setup data files, also
	handling of JK signon from any email account, adjustment of
	takeover countries as according to game settings (deadline that is)
	Showing of preference and absence settings on signon (the first
	restricted to master only) Handling of BLankBoard games (where game
	starts with no pieces)

