	* dip.c: Many changes, including -   Reminding players to make
	moves when close to deadline   Special handling for blind games  
	Passing of '-C' option for specifying dip.conf path   Informaing
	all masters when a time-warp was detected   Handling of NOLATEPRESS
	and MANUALSTART flags	Adding automatic wati for all players in a
	build phase of a transform game

2000-11-14 09:27  miller

	* ml_press.c: Various changes including  - Partial press between
	master and only one power is NOT sent to others with WATCHALL set 
	- Rejct press in a monor phase when XF_NOMINORPRESS is set  -
	Change press handling to allow observers to press  in no-press
	games f allowed (i.e. BackSeat Driver variant)	- Add prevention of
	press from late players, if flag is set

